cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper discusses language processing and conceptual grounding of language. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is also likely as the paper discusses multimodal processing which involves visual information. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another likely category as the paper discusses cognitive models of human information processing and methods for combining multimodal representations. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also possible as the paper discusses different methods for combining multimodal representations and the benefit of multimodal grounding for language processing tasks. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is less likely but still possible as the paper may discuss neural models for multimodal processing and language processing.
